The Damned United;;85;;92;;R;;The story of Brian Clough's 44 day stint as manager of Leeds United Football Club takes place in 1974 England. When Don Revie quits Leeds to become the England boss, the outspoken Brian Clough takes charge. Determined to impose his own style upon Revie's tough tackling team, Clough soon alienates his players and the board. Based on the book by David Pearce.;;Drama,Biography;;Tom Hooper;;2009;;Michael Sheen,Timothy Spall,Jim Broadbent,Stephen Graham,Joe Dempsie,Colm Meaney,Martin Compston,Maurice RoÃ«ves,Elizabeth Carling,Brian McCardie,Peter McDonald,Giles Anderson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/damned_united